Dental Lab Services: Partnership Built on Precision and Speed

Headline: Minimize Chair Time. Maximize Patient Satisfaction. Partner with Next Gen Dental.

Introduction: Your In-House, High-Speed Solution

Next Gen Dental isn't just a lab; we're an extension of your practice. Leveraging our on-site prosthetist expertise and advanced digital workflows, we guarantee not only Trusted Quality but also the rapid turnaround times required to keep your practice efficient and your patients happy.

We specialize in precision-fabricated removable appliances with an emphasis on flawless fit from the first try-in.

Our Core Laboratory Services

We offer comprehensive support for common removable needs, crafted with both traditional and digital CAD/CAM methodologies.

1. Precision Dentures (Full and Partial)

Focus: Superior aesthetics, retention, and occlusion.

Advantage: Our dual function as a clinic gives us unique insights into clinical fit, translating to exceptional lab work and fewer adjustments required in your chair.

2. Orthodontic Retainers

Focus: Durable, accurate retainers essential for maintaining post-treatment results.

Advantage: Fast digital fabrication processes ensure quick delivery, preventing case relapse.

3. Splints and Nightguards

Focus: Comfortable, custom-fitted appliances for bruxism and TMD management.

Advantage: Consistent material quality and precise fit based on exact impression or scan data.

4. Custom Sports Mouthguards

Focus: Individually molded protection for athletes.

Advantage: Quick, reliable service so patients can return to play safely and without delay.

